{"tid":2405842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登：美國若不加快步伐將被中國擊敗","createTime":"2021-02-12T16:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T00:34:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6a52e9503bf2b3955fdef786da4914e991fd95a9","tid":2405842,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平周三與美國總統拜登通電話兩小時。拜登在白宮表示，兩人對話良好，他又指，中國在基建等多方面投資，美國如果不加快步伐，將會被擊敗。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，繼TikTok後，美國司法部再宣布，暫緩就中國通訊軟件WeChat案件上訴。前總統特朗普政府去年以威脅國家安全為由，頒令要求禁用兩個軟件，被法院駁回。特朗普政府之後提出上訴。美國司法部表示，如今暫緩上訴，是要重新評估軟件有否真正威脅國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575478-20210212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575478-20210212.htm&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=e2c9f1d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575478-20210212.htm&h=7af83782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575478-20210212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6a6c93c33ece002d1cc80df64820a4293973e67c","tid":2405842,"uid":125017,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/1oBR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F1oBR.gif&h=0c76efdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae8db3289fa077de5817df3a6d548abde9aec6ce","tid":2405842,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a6c93c33ece002d1cc80df64820a4293973e67c","tid":2405842,"uid":125017,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/1oBR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F1oBR.gif&h=0c76efdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a